是一起企图在胜利日前夕暗杀普京的行动。 乌克兰方面则表示此事与乌无关。乌克兰总统办公室顾问波多利亚克表示，乌方没有袭击克里姆林宫，乌方袭击目标仅限于乌被占领土上的军事设施。乌总统泽连斯基本人也公开表态，称“乌克兰没有攻击普京或莫斯科”，且没有能力做到这一点。 同日，美国白宫发言人卡琳·让-皮埃尔表示，美国没有鼓励或允许乌克兰攻击其境外的目标。美智库战争研究所：克宫遭无人机袭击可能是俄“自导自演”_全球速报_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"Cj8IidD73uLS3+IzEAMaCDk1NDMxNzQwIMb/0aIGMAk4iwFAB3IJNTk5MTc5OTYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d6dc4a6827c997a5087b292ec48d7bfe_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1683414845.4392004","card_id":"Q_325706798","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":325706798,"title":"中国在化学领域让你最引以为豪的成果是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/325706798","type":"question","created":1558593940,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":335,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1027,2143,2232,4217],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"可以说说这个成果的前因后果和影响吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IidD73uLS3+IzEAMaCDM0NjU1MjIzIJSDmecFMAU4zwJACHIJMzI1NzA2Nzk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-617f4f6cafc577a36fa752714a03255f_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1683414845.4397826","card_id":"Q_597409944","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":597409944,"title":"2023年618打算换手机，3000元以内有什么高性价比手机推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/597409944","type":"question","created":1682290830,"answer_count":91,"follower_count":199,"author"